University Library


Services


Request Items






Request Items
Staff, students, faculty and emeritus faculty can request items from other libraries.






            Text block
          Heading link



 
Copy link



I-Share will quickly deliver physical items from Illinois academic libraries.   Interlibrary Loan (ILLiad) allows you to request scanned articles and items not available in I-Share.
If you have trouble logging in, please see setting up a Library account.  If you still have trouble, contact us.





            Request Items links
          Heading link



 
Copy link









                            Search I-Share
                    

                Request books and media
            









                            Login to ILLiad
                    

                Request scanned articles and items from libraries worldwide
            










            I-Share: Request books and media
          Heading link



 
Copy link




Search I-Share for an item
Sign in (top left)
Click on what you need!
Click “GET IT FROM OTHER INSTITUTIONS”

Do you need your item sent to a library closer to you?  Change the “preferred pick-up location” to any institution participating in I-Share. You’ll get an email when the item is ready to pick up, usually in 3-5 business days.






            Interlibrary Loan (ILLiad): request scanned articles and items from libraries worldwide
          Heading link



 
Copy link




Login to ILLiad
Create a request manually or automatically:

Manual request: See New Request menu on the left, enter or copy and paste citation.
Auto-fill an article request:

Click Find it @ UIC in library databases or in Google Scholar.
Click Request via inter library loan.





UIC School of Law patrons can make ILL requests through a separate ILL system.






            Interlibrary Loan tutorial
          Heading link



 
Copy link


















            Alumni
          Heading link



 
Copy link



We cannot offer I-Share or interlibrary loan services to alumni.
Alumni may order documents from the UIC Library collection for a fee; please contact us for more information.






